oai_dc:dc.dc:title: "Portion of Record Breaking Crowd Which Saw M.U.S. Beat C.H.S."
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Central High School; schools; football; sports; Russwood Park; crowds; 1920s;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A newspaper clipping from the Commerical Appeal showing a photograph of the crowd which gathered at Russwood Park to watch the annual Thanksgiving day football game between Central High School and Memphis University School.
